<h4 id="dynamic-programming-solutiongtop-to-down">Dynamic Programming Solutiong(Top to down)</h4>

\[g(i, s)=\min _{k \in S}\left\{c_{i k}+g(k, s-\{k\})\right\}\]

<h4 id="2-recursive-tree">2. Recursive Tree</h4>
<p><img src="/images/computer-science-algorithm-problem-traveling-salesman.png" /></p>

<h4 id="3-recursive-table">3. Recursive Table</h4>

\[\begin{array}{l}g(2, \phi)=5 \\ g(3, \phi)=6 \\ g(4,\phi)=8\end{array}\]

\[\begin{array}{l}g(2,\{3\})=15 \\ g(2,\{4\})=18 \\ g(3,\{2\})=18 \\ g(3,\{4\})=20
\\ g(4,\{2\})=13 \\ g(4,\{3\})=15\end{array}\]

\[\begin{array}{l}
g(2,\{3,4\})=25 \\ 
g(3,\{2,4\})=25 \\ 
g(4,\{2,3\})=23 \\
g(1,\{2,3,4\})=35 \\
\end{array}\]

